WEBVTT

00:01.171 --> 00:01.931
Give her some room.

00:01.932 --> 00:03.350
She needs space! Breathe, girl, breathe!

00:03.372 --> 00:04.736
Does anyone have anything she can eat?

00:04.737 --> 00:06.777
I have some leftover
Halloween candy in my locker.

00:06.778 --> 00:08.778
I may have a juice box.
I'll go get Marley's mom.

00:08.779 --> 00:09.579
ARTIE:
This is bad.

00:09.580 --> 00:10.535
Never in the history

00:10.553 --> 00:13.872
of show choir competitions
has anyone ever fainted.

00:13.890 --> 00:16.201
We got the juice.
We got the juice.

00:16.202 --> 00:17.642
No, I'm okay.
Drink the damn juice!

00:17.643 --> 00:19.683
FINN: Marley? Marley, are you okay?
What happened?

00:19.684 --> 00:20.884
JAKE:
She hasn't been eating.

00:20.885 --> 00:21.783
She's been skipping lunch.

00:21.784 --> 00:22.384
Is that because

00:22.385 --> 00:23.465
you've been telling her to?

00:23.466 --> 00:24.346
You trying to turn her

00:24.347 --> 00:25.717
into a damn rexy?
What?

00:25.735 --> 00:27.415
No. Why would I...
why would I want that?

00:27.416 --> 00:28.776
'Cause you're a crazy, evil bitch.

00:28.777 --> 00:29.857
Hey, Marley, you all right?

00:29.858 --> 00:32.978
The nurse is on the way, Mr. Schue.
Santana, Puck, you stay here with Marley.

00:32.979 --> 00:34.619
The rest of you guys,
get back up there.

00:34.620 --> 00:36.020
Leaving the stage
mid-competition,

00:36.021 --> 00:38.221
for any reason, is risking
immediate disqualification.

00:38.222 --> 00:39.564
What?! That-that's a rule?

00:39.582 --> 00:40.783
SUE:
Yeah, it's a rule.

00:40.834 --> 00:42.451
One of the bylaws, actually.

00:42.502 --> 00:43.782
As all of you all were spiraling

00:43.783 --> 00:46.738
into a self-created
K-hole of crazy,

00:46.756 --> 00:48.173
the judges, by unanimous vote,

00:48.208 --> 00:51.009
have declared the Warblers victorious.

00:53.279 --> 00:54.639
Hey, congratulations, Finn Hudson.

00:54.640 --> 00:56.000
For the first time in its charmed,

00:56.001 --> 00:57.132
yet pitiful existence,

00:57.183 --> 00:58.917
the New Directions!
Has lost Sectionals.

00:58.935 --> 01:00.469
But here's the good news.

01:00.520 --> 01:03.138
Christmas came early
for one Sue Sylvester.

01:11.834 --> 01:14.415
